 dispose of other items"],"\n\n    \n\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"rich-text"},["P",{"data-block-key":"0m674"},"Find out how to dispose of small household electricals, batteries and textiles."]],"\n    \n\n    \n        \n\n",["DIV",{"class":"accordion__container","id":"09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a"},"\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"accordion","data-accordion":""},"\n            ",["H3",{"class":"accordion__header"},"\n                ",["BUTTON",{"id":"question-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-1","class":"accordion__button","data-accordion-question":"","aria-controls":"answer-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-1","aria-expanded":"false"},"\n                    \n",["svg",{"class":"icon icon-chevron icon--stroke accordion__icon","aria-hidden":"true","focusable":"false"},"\n    ",["use",{"xlink:href":"#chevron"}],"\n"],"\n\n                    ",["SPAN",{"class":"accordion__title"},"\n                        Small household electricals\n                    "],"\n                "],"\n            "],"\n            ",["DIV",{"id":"answer-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-1","role":"region","data-accordion-answer":"","class":"accordion__content","aria-labelledby":"question-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-1","hidden":"until-found"},"\n                \n\n\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"rich-text"},["P",{"data-block-key":"6sevl"},"You can recycle small electrical items on top of your household recycling bins."],["P",{"data-block-key":"7fb16"},"We can collect any small electrical items such as hairdryers, toys and mobile devices. Small household electricals will have one of the below:"],["UL",{},["LI",{"data-block-key":"cv6ka"},"plug"],["LI",{"data-block-key":"bthj2"},"battery"],["LI",{"data-block-key":"dht51"},"charger"]],["P",{"data-block-key":"85fer"},"Leave any unwanted small electrical items on top of your recycling bin, in a standard carrier bag, on your collection day. Do not put electrical items in the bin. The crews will collect your items at the same time as they empty your bins."],["P",{"data-block-key":"5er4e"},"If you live in the Aylesbury Vale area, you can only recycle electrical items smaller than a shoebox. You can place these items on your bin lid on either waste or recycling collection. The collection vehicles have limited space which means we can only collect smaller electrical items."],["P",{"data-block-key":"fd2lf"},"You can take larger electrical items, such as TVs and microwaves to your nearest ",["A",{"href":"https://www.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/bin-collection-recycling-and-waste/find-your-nearest-household-recycling-centre/"},"household recycling centre"]," or you can arrange a ",["A",{"href":"https://www.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/waste-and-recycling/book-a-bulky-waste-collection/"},"bulky waste collection"],". There is a fee for this service."]],"\n    \n\n\n            "],"\n        "],"\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"accordion","data-accordion":""},"\n            ",["H3",{"class":"accordion__header"},"\n                ",["BUTTON",{"id":"question-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-2","class":"accordion__button","data-accordion-question":"","aria-controls":"answer-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-2","aria-expanded":"false"},"\n                    \n",["svg",{"class":"icon icon-chevron icon--stroke accordion__icon","aria-hidden":"true","focusable":"false"},"\n    ",["use",{"xlink:href":"#chevron"}],"\n"],"\n\n                    ",["SPAN",{"class":"accordion__title"},"\n                        Batteries\n                    "],"\n                "],"\n            "],"\n            ",["DIV",{"id":"answer-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-2","role":"region","data-accordion-answer":"","class":"accordion__content","aria-labelledby":"question-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-2","hidden":"until-found"},"\n                \n\n\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"rich-text"},["P",{"data-block-key":"6sevl"},"Do not put batteries in your bins."],["P",{"data-block-key":"6ij22"},"You can use our kerbside service to recycle most household batteries but they must be kept ",["B",{},"separate"]," from your other waste and recycling."],["P",{"data-block-key":"eu0dv"},"Place batteries loose in small clear bags and put the bags on top of any bin on collection day. You can use any type of clear bag."]],"\n    \n\n    \n        ",["H3",{"class":"heading heading--m","id":"batteries-we-can-collect"},"Batteries we can collect"],"\n\n    \n\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"rich-text"},["P",{"data-block-key":"6sevl"},"We can collect:"],["UL",{},["LI",{"data-block-key":"a7i79"},"household batteries"],["LI",{"data-block-key":"573s6"},"mobile phone batteries"],["LI",{"data-block-key":"2c5oj"},"laptop batteries"],["LI",{"data-block-key":"4ii2k"},"power tool batteries"]]],"\n    \n\n    \n        ",["H3",{"class":"heading heading--m","id":"batteries-we-cant-collect"},"Batteries we can't collect"],"\n\n    \n\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"rich-text"},["P",{"data-block-key":"6sevl"},"We can't collect:"],["UL",{},["LI",{"data-block-key":"b32nq"},"damaged or leaking batteries"],["LI",{"data-block-key":"eimu9"},"car batteries - take these to a ",["A",{"href":"https://www.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/bin-collection-recycling-and-waste/find-your-nearest-household-recycling-centre/"},"household recycling centre"]],["LI",{"data-block-key":"o5fo"},"industrial batteries"]]],"\n    \n\n\n            "],"\n        "],"\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"accordion","data-accordion":""},"\n            ",["H3",{"class":"accordion__header"},"\n                ",["BUTTON",{"id":"question-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-3","class":"accordion__button","data-accordion-question":"","aria-controls":"answer-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-3","aria-expanded":"false"},"\n                    \n",["svg",{"class":"icon icon-chevron icon--stroke accordion__icon","aria-hidden":"true","focusable":"false"},"\n    ",["use",{"xlink:href":"#chevron"}],"\n"],"\n\n                    ",["SPAN",{"class":"accordion__title"},"\n                        Textiles\n                    "],"\n                "],"\n            "],"\n            ",["DIV",{"id":"answer-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-3","role":"region","data-accordion-answer":"","class":"accordion__content","aria-labelledby":"question-09eedfb8-bdbe-473b-91a1-2e24f9c1ef6a-3","hidden":"until-found"},"\n                \n\n\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"rich-text"},["P",{"data-block-key":"6sevl"},"All clothes and home textiles can be recycled as long as they are clean and dry."],["P",{"data-block-key":"1j0q6"},"Textiles can be disposed of at household recycling centres or textile banks."],["P",{"data-block-key":"3kmcj"},"Use the ",["A",{"href":"https://www.recycleforbuckinghamshire.co.uk/waste-wizard/"},"Waste Wizard"]," to find out where to recycle textiles."],["P",{"data-block-key":"a3elq"},"If you live in the Chiltern or Wycombe areas, you can ",["A",{"href":"https://www.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/waste-and-recycling/new-and-replacement-bins-boxes-or-sacks/order-textile-recycling-sacks/"},"order textile sacks"]," which we will collect on your recycling collection day."],["P",{"data-block-key":"cbtiv"},"If you live in South Bucks use a standard carrier bag and place this alongside your bins on your recycling collection day. Avoid using bin liners because our crews might mistake them for general waste."],["P",{"data-block-key":"76inp"},"If you live in the Aylesbury area, textile kerbside collections are not available."]],"\n    \n\n\n            "],"\n        "],"\n    \n"],"\n\n\n    \n\n    \n        ",["H2",{"class":"heading heading--l","id":"extra-waste-and-recycling"},"Extra waste and recycling"],"\n\n    \n\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"rich-text"},["P",{"data-block-key":"0m674"},"We will only collect general waste that fits in your bin with the bin lid closed."],["P",{"data-block-key":"audug"},"We can collect a reasonable amount of extra recycling that doesn’t fit in your box or bin. To help us collect extra recycling:"],["UL",{},["LI",{"data-block-key":"8d27p"},"put it in a reusable container, such as a plastic box, so that we can tip it out - we will not collect recyclables in plastic bags"],["LI",{"data-block-key":"cfjv1"},"leave it neatly beside your usual recycling box, bag or bin"],["LI",{"data-block-key":"50usk"},"cut down and flatten cardboard boxes to a manageable size (less than 1 metre by 1 metre), remove all other packaging (such as polystyrene or plastic inserts) and place next to your bin"]],["P",{"data-block-key":"brflg"},"Take any extra recycling or waste to your nearest ",["A",{"href":"https://www.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/bin-collection-recycling-and-waste/find-your-nearest-household-recycling-centre/"},"household recycling centre"],"."]],"\n    \n\n    \n        \n\n",["DIV",{"class":"image-block"},"\n    \n    \n    \n    ",["PICTURE",{"__playwright_current_src__":""},"\n    ",["SOURCE",{"srcset":"https://media.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/images/Waste.width-650.png","media":"(min-width: 768px)"}],"\n    ",["SOURCE",{"srcset":"https://media.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/images/Waste.width-400.png, https://media.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/images/Waste.width-800.png 2x"}],"\n    ",["IMG",{"__playwright_current_src__":"https://media.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/images/Waste.width-650.png","src":"https://media.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/images/Waste.width-650.png","alt":""}],"\n"],"\n\n    ",["P",{"class":"image-block__caption"},"Images showing how extra recycling should be presented to be collected by waste crews"],"\n"],"\n\n    \n\n    \n        ",["H2",{"class":"heading heading--l","id":"bin-collection-days"},"Bin collection days"],"\n\n    \n\n    \n        ",["DIV",{"class":"rich-text"},["P",{"data-block-key":"glgbk"},["A",{"href":"https://www.buckinghamshire.gov.uk/waste-and-recycling/find-out-when-its-your-bin-collection/"},"Check your bin collection day"]]],"\n    \n\n    \n        ",["H2",{"class":"heading heading--l","id":"view-our-policy"},"